Amber Heard And Jared Leto Will Lead Zack Snyder’s Justice League 2

This latest Amber Heard and Jared Leto rumor comes as we lead into the event that will be Zack Snyder’s Justice League premiering on HBO Max later this month. Whenever there is something this big in the works it always happens that rumors get out about what’s planned next.
